hen they were as qualified as white applicants for the same jobs palantir settled the suit in april  for  million while not admitting wrongdoing see alsoedit recorded future referencesedit  hardy quentin may   unlocking secrets if not its own value the new york times retrieved    a b buhr sarah december   palantir has raised  million at a  billion valuation techcrunch   a b c d gorman siobhan september   how team of geeks cracked spy trade the wall street journal   a b c d a tech fix for illegal government snooping npr retrieved    a b a pretty complete history of palantir maus strategic consulting retrieved    a b c d e f g mac ryan december   palantir aiming to raise  million in new round forbes retrieved    sec form d securities and exchange commission retrieved    greenberg andy mac ryan august   how a deviant philosopher built palantir a ciafunded datamining juggernaut forbes   charlierose mediapalantirtechcom retrieved    palantir technologies  crunchbase profile crunchbasecom retrieved    contact information   palantir « founders fund founders’ fund retrieved    evelyn rusli  palantir the next billiondollar company raises  million techcrunch retrieved    a b alexander karp charlie rose  retrieved    widman jeff  palantir keeps it lean and mean on fiveyear journey from zero to  employees venturebeat retrieved    gesher ari  friction in humancomputer symbiosis kasparov on chess palantir tech retrieved    video cnn   a b c chiang oliver  paypalbased technology helped bust indias and the dalai lamas cyberspies forbes   markoff john march   vast spy system loots computers in  countries the new york times   press release thomson reuters and palantir technologies enter exclusive agreement to create nextgeneration analytics platform for financial clients thomson reuters    tim kauffman  the new hightech weapons against fraud federal times retrieved    kiely kathy  obama administration to create do not pay list to bar shady contractors usa today   peter orszag directo