competing on if were competing in some athletic event for competitive swimmers really intensely competing its likely that both of us will become better but its also quite possible well lose sight of whats truly valuable peter thiel competition people better its good to test yourself and develop your talents and ambitions as fully as you can and achieve greater success but i think success is the feeling you get from a job well done and the key thing is to do the work peter thiel work success good technology just means information technology peter thiel technology information if you do something new it will always look a little bit strange peter thiel strange look you it is true that you can say that death is natural but it is also natural to fight death but if you stand up and say this is a big problem we should do something about this that makes people very uncomfortable because theyve made their peace with death peter thiel death peace fight the future is limitless peter thiel future limitless in a world where wealth is growing you can get away with printing money doubling the debt over the next  years is not a problem peter thiel money world problem in the s the keynesian stuff worked at least in the sense that you could print money without inflation because there was all this productivity growth happening thats not going to work today peter thiel work money today people dont want to believe that technology is broken pharmaceuticals robotics artificial intelligence nanotechnology  all these areas where the progress has been a lot more limited than people think and the question is why peter thiel technology progress broken i believe we are in a world where innovation in stuff was outlawed it was basically outlawed in the last  years  part of it was environmentalism part of it was risk aversion peter thiel innovation risk world had the people who started facebook decided to stay at harvard they would not have been able to build the company and by the time they graduated in  that window probably would have come and gone peter thiel time window people people always say you should live your life as if it were your last day i think you should live your life as though it will go on for ever that every day is so good that you dont want it to end peter thiel life good day theres always a sense that people will do things quite differently if they think they have privacy peter thiel people think privacy top  peter thiel quotes view the list every time you write an email it is in the public domain there are all these ways where security is not as good as people believe peter thiel time good believe in silicon valley i point out that many of the more successful entrepreneurs seem to be suffering from a mild form of aspergers where its like youre missing the imitation socialization gene peter thiel successful suffering you from my perspective i think the question of how we build a better future is an extremely important overarching question and i think its become obscured from us because we no longer think its possible to have a meaningful conversation about the future peter thiel future perspective better facebook succeeded because it was about real people having a presence on the internet there were all these other social networking sites people had but they were all about fictional people peter thiel networking people internet i think whats always important is not to be contrarian for its own sake but to really get at the truth peter thiel truth important think the core problem in our society is political correctness peter thiel society problem political dont bother starting the th restaurant in manhattan find something to do that if you dont do it it wont get done peter thiel restaurant you done we live in a world in which courage is in less supply than genius peter thiel courage world genius i do think there is this danger that our society has made its peace with decline id like to jolt them out of their complacency a little bit peter thiel peace society complacency a diploma is a dunce hat in disguise peter thiel hat diploma disguise we protect monopolies with copyright peter thiel protect copyright what is it about our society where anyone who does not have aspergers gets talked out of their heterodox ideas peter thiel society ideas our theres absolutely no bubble in technology peter thiel technology bubble share this page cite this page citation find on amazon peter thiel related authors steve jobs warren buffett henry ford bill gates jim rohn stephen covey peter drucker les brown brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of the day pictures top  quotes professions birthdays social bq on facebook bq on twitter bq on pinterest bq on google bq on instagram shop brainyquote store apps iphoneipad app quote of the day feeds javascript and rss feeds wordpress plugin quote of the day email about about us contact us submit privacy terms copyright     brainyquote   loading load more quotes